        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We can discuss how specific onchain products fit within the SFC framework for your firm.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們可以討論特定鏈上產品如何在SFC框架下適用於你的公司。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
